window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They call me mad, but I don’t see anything wrong with using science to create the perfect monster girl.</p> <p>They call me insane, but I just want to live my life with a harem of beautiful cat-girls, bear-girls, fox-girls, snake-girls, and...well, pretty much any type of monster girl.</p> <p>They call me a megalomaniac, but why wouldn’t any red blooded man want to make cute babies with all these beautiful monster girls?</p> <p>They call me evil, but they just don’t realize that I’d destroy anyone who tries to harm my monster girls.</p>"; 
